<div style="background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px">

<p>&nbsp; server_name&nbsp; haha.linlin.fun;</p>
<p>&nbsp; charset utf-8;</p>
<p>&nbsp; location / {<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; root /tmp/build;<br />
&nbsp; }</p>
<p>&nbsp; location /blog/ {&nbsp; # 这一段也需要设置，不然博客详情页面不能正常访问<br />
